de.feu.showgo.io

Class PseudoRoleRecognition

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feu.showgo.io.PseudoRoleRecognition

  • public class PseudoRoleRecognition
extends java.lang.Object
    A class containing logic for recognizing pseudo-roles in a TheaterPlay object in the role name. Currently it recognizes roles combined with und (german for and) like "MAC BETH und LADY MAC BETH", enumerations "HEXE 1, HEXE 2 und HEXE 3" and the all roles a scene are filled.
